snippet.title: Monarchies of Wax and Honey Gameplay Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Play as a bee queen in this real-time top-down simulation game. Lay eggs to begin building up your hive. Command your workers to build new hive cells, forage flowers for nectar and pollen, nurse pupae into more workers, and defend the hive against wasps and other colonies.  Complete challenges or play in sandbox mode. Unlock new species and skins to play as.

Play for free in a browser at:
https://monarchies.io/

Available on the Play Store:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.monarchies
